author: brane
msg: Hmmm, whoever decided to call the unspecified revision "START"?
Free speech is all very well, but at least we could follow naming conventions.
(Revision.UNSPECIFIED): Make an alias for Revision.START, so that developers
familiar with Subversion's API have a chance of undertanding JavaHL, too.
